-- Juncker: looking how EFSF can have 440 billion euros available
-- 
-- Mon Jan 17, 2011 6:34pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/01/17/us-eurozone-juncker-idUSTRE70G5V720110117

 

 BRUSSELS  (Reuters) - Euro zone finance ministers and EU officials met on Monday to discuss the euro zone rescue fund, to try to draw a line under the sovereign debt crisis before more countries need help. 

